# Local Stack

## Environment

- **OS**: macOS (darwin)
- **Shell**: Zsh (primary), Fish (alternative)
- **Terminal**: Cursor/VSCode embedded (primary), Warp, iTerm2, Terminal.app

## Dotfiles Management

- **Manager**: [Rotz](https://github.com/volllly/rotz) - dotfiles manager with templating
- **Config**: `config.yaml` for variables and linking configuration
- **Structure**: `dot.yaml` files in each tool directory

## Package Managers

- **Homebrew**: System packages and CLI tools
- **mise**: Runtime version management (node, python, go, terraform, etc.)
- **uv**: Python project management
- **Zinit**: Zsh plugin manager
- **Fisher**: Fish plugin manager

## Key Tools

- **Editor**: Cursor, VSCode, Neovim
- **Git**: gh CLI, 1Password SSH agent
- **Search**: fzf, fd, ripgrep
- **Shell**: starship prompt, eza, bat
